      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-quality specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. The valvetrain is meticulously calibrated with recent shim adjustments, and the double VANOS system has been fully overhauled for optimal cam phasing. The rear subframe mounting points have been structurally reinforced, ensuring chassis rigidity and long-term durability. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with fresh bushings and dampers, delivering the tactile feedback expected of a flagship M-car. With no cosmetic oxidation or paint depth inconsistencies, this is a superlative, turn-key example for the discerning enthusiast.",
